Package providing a set of tools for debugging python code with gdb

Tested with Python 2.7.5

Dependencies:
=============
gdb python: https://wiki.python.org/moin/DebuggingWithGdb
C compiler (e.g. gcc), Python development headers,

Install:
=================
pip install .
ln -sf .gdbinit ~/

Uninstall:
=================
pip uninstall pygdb
rm -f ~/.gdbinit
